{
  "stem": "15115.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the second-- second attempt I made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got into Innsbruck, me and my friend David.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had the money rolled up, like dollars rolled up in the seam of my-- what do you call it-- of my undershirt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hide them over here, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Cross the border, sure enough, the French caught us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My-- my friend had the money in a safe, a regular safe, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he had them in his pocket, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the French took the rucksacks, so they saw some-- we had some grappa, which is whiskey, nice-- so they took it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put the-- they searched me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have anything, because everything was hidden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my friend's safe, took them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He put them on the table, said, how you going to use this, eh?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he didn't see the money inside, [BACKGROUND NOISE] you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is somebody here?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they found out it was-- they didn't catch it, so-- we got-- we got it back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got back into Feldafing, back into the Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Ah, I got sick from the mountains, you know, the snow and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a woman from the UNRRA-- which we had there, they were looking after us-- saw me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, you-- when I told them the story what happened, you know, through the mountains-- and I was sick, really sick, weak.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Says I'm going to send you for holiday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He sends me for two weeks in Garmisch-Partenkirchen, which is a-- a ski resort, just about 80, 90 kilometers from Feldafing, in the mountains, a gorgeous place, like a palace.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, I had bought a lot of stuff to take back with me to Italy.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
